title: Rush The Growler - RTG
description:
Rush The Growler

Musicians are Jim Golden, Tim Butt, Ryan Lafleche, Dave McCrank, and Adam Gilbert.

I found this CD at a thrift store for a couple bucks. Bought it because it looked interesting, I think they might be Canadian, judging by the images. Great rock sound. A little grungy maybe? Not too much though. Some of the acoustic is amazing, makes me think.

If ANYONE know ANYTHING about these guys please message me. I think they are awesome and I don't know anything about them. The only thing I know is that they are from 1996. Anyway, enjoy the music, it's great.

Please Seed, I'll try to seed as much as possible, but I can't always leave my laptop on.
